[this one is written on a Nazi propaganda postcard.]

April 1, 1945
Germany

Dearest Folks,

Was sure glad to get a couple of letters from you today, with Sons address enclosed. I'll drop him a line right away.

Well we didn't have too much from this Easter instead of hunting eggs, we hunted Nazis. only a little luck tho.

The German army isn't in quite so good condition now as the picture shows. As you know by now. Write often Love O.L.